comments.text:
Need to know our "roots" on https://graphite-phx.mozilla.org/render/

e.g., AMO has:

        'roots': {
                'timers': ['stats.timers.addons-dev', 'stats.timers.addons'],
                'counts': ['stats.addons-dev', 'stats.addons']
        }

We probably want different roots for staging and production like:

        'roots': {
                'timers': ['stats.timers.developer-allizom', 'stats.timers.developer'],
                'counts': ['stats.developer-allizom', 'stats.developer']
        }
